WEBVTT

00:02.955 --> 00:06.211
Are you going to in-line skate in the park?

00:07.344 --> 00:11.494
No, I can't go in-line skating because I have a cold.

00:11.939 --> 00:16.589
Instead of in-line skating, I'm going to read scary stories at home.

00:19.655 --> 00:21.683
Why don't we go to the beach?

00:22.107 --> 00:25.266
I will gather shells to make sand castles.

00:26.447 --> 00:30.185
My mom is busy. So I have to help her clean the house.

00:33.263 --> 00:35.462
What are you going to do this weekend?

00:36.618 --> 00:40.479
I will visit my grandma to celebrate her 60th birthday.

00:40.757 --> 00:41.805
What about you?

00:42.901 --> 00:47.453
I have to take care of my brother because he is sick in bed.

